responses: {"Q0":"I was trying to be smart about how i gambled with the blue vs green choices but at the end of the day it was still a gamble, i would choose a few blues hoping to get lucky with 70 and if i hit 2 in the round without hitting a 30 i considered myself \"up\" so then went greens to stay ahead, if i fell behind i would try to get back to a net positive as if i had choose green the whole round."}
